# PlayerBet - Sports Betting Platform

A modern sports betting web application built with React frontend and .NET backend with PostgreSQL database.

## Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 18+ and npm
- .NET 8.0 SDK
- PostgreSQL 14+
- Docker (optional)

### Frontend Setup
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm start
```

### Backend Setup
```bash
cd backend/PlayerBet.Api
dotnet restore
dotnet run
```

### Docker Setup
```bash
docker-compose up -d
```

## Project Structure

```
playerbet-app/
├── frontend/
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── pages/
│   │   ├── components/
